						"description": "Creates a new account at the Intergalactic Bank.\n\n### Request Body Properties\n\n| Property Name | Property Type | **Description** | **Required?** |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| owner | String | Full name of the person opening this account | Yes |\n| balance | Number | The starting balance of the account | Yes |\n| currency | String - Possible values: `COSMIC_COINS`, `GALAXY_GOLD`, `MOON_BUCKS` | The currency this account will be using for transactions. This cannot be changed once established. | Yes |\n\n### Response\n\nA successful request will contain a single `account` object with the newly created account `id`"
